data.title: Early life of an actress of absorbing honesty
data.meta_description: On Barbara Stanwyck's birthday in 1939, her husband, Robert Taylor, was at the studio doing retakes. Two weeks later on his natal day (she was 32, he 28), they celebrated both events over an intimate dinner.
